sights.name: DIVA
sights.quote: Modern venue with themed rooms showcasing diamonds, gold, silver & gemstones, plus summer workshops.

sights.name: De Ruien
sights.quote: Wellies are provided for this wet, subterranean guided tour of historic former canals & sewers.

sights.name: Museum aan de Stroom
sights.quote: Striking red sandstone museum with high-tech exhibitions exploring Antwerp's place in the world.
